        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Well you have to understand the \"initial plan\" is very succinct, to the point of being non-obvious to outsiders. As I said, the intent is very obvious, but not the form. Are we talking about a new layout engine? I vaguely remember from other conceal-related issues that this direction was considered a non-starter.",
