            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> Are we talking about a new layout engine?\n\nthat is orthogonal. presentation mode will take advantage of new UI features as they arrive. it's simply a way to switch on things that otherwise might conflict with \"editing\".\n\nthe problem statement says it clearly:\n\n> we have to choose between optimizing for editing instead of viewing.",
